Source.Name: mojave-gtk-theme
Source.Summary: Mojave is a macos Mojave like theme for GTK 3, GTK 2 and Gnome-Shell
Source.Description: Mojave is a Mac OSX like theme for GTK 3, GTK 2 and Gnome-Shell which supports GTK 3 and GTK 2 based desktop environments like Gnome, Budgie and Mate.
